  "prompt": "Where can I search for best five star hotel in Bhopal?",
  "response": "To find the best five-star hotels in Bhopal, you can use various online resources and platforms:\n\n1. **Google Search**: Simply typing \"best five-star hotels in Bhopal\" in Google will give you a quick overview along with reviews, ratings, and locations.\n\n2. **TripAdvisor**: This platform offers detailed reviews and ratings from travelers, helping you decide based on their experiences.\n\n3. **Booking.com**: You can search for five-star hotels in Bhopal, compare prices, check availability, and read reviews.\n\n4. **Expedia**: Another option for finding and booking five-star hotels with user reviews and ratings.\n\n5. **MakeMyTrip**: This is an India-specific travel website that lists hotels, offering deals and customer feedback.\n\n6. **Agoda**: Known for competitive rates, you can search for luxury accommodations and read guest reviews.\n\n7. **Yelp**: Although not as commonly used for hotel searches in India, it can sometimes provide useful reviews.\n\n8. **Zomato**: While primarily a restaurant app, some hotel dining options appear here with reviews.\n\nAdditionally, you can directly visit the websites of well-known hotel chains and luxury hotels present in Bhopal to check their offerings and customer feedback.",
